videos.description: After trailing by 27 points with a little under 12 minutes to play, Eastern Illinois comes back to beat Murray State on Josiah Wallace's buzzer-beating 3-pointer 63-60.
videos.headline: Wallace's buzzer-beating 3 caps off Eastern Illinois' 27-point comeback
